A4.text: He later went solo and recorded 'The Birds and the Bees' in 1964, on the Era Records label.

A5.text: The single went to Number 3 in the Billboard Hot 100 chart that year, and Number 2 on the Cash Box chart, and was Number 2 for four weeks on Canada's CHUM Chart
